# REPORT: AGENT 1 (FULL_STACK_IMPLEMENTER)

Summary: Reviewed Sprint 5/6 plan card consolidation and implemented PremiumCard variants for default/glass/outline/adhd/metric/stat; removed "Total Events" brag metric in Sentry reports view and replaced with a simple System Status indicator.

